Title: Chapter 66
Writer: Michael Dobbs (based on the novels by), Andrew Davies (based on the mini-series by), Beau Willimon (created for television by), Melissa James Gibson, Frank Pugliese, Tian Jun Gu (story editor), Sharon Hoffman (story editor)
